### Phase 1: Phishing Infrastructure Setup

To simulate a phishing attack, we set up a cloned OAuth endpoint to capture user credentials.

1. Clone the OAuth authorization endpoint: `https://example.com/oauth/authorize` becomes `https://attacker.com/oauth/authorize`.
2. Configure an SMTP server to deliver phishing payloads.

```rust
